  <p>
    Q-Tune is the only precision chromatic tuner available as a DIY pedal kit. It pairs a 2.8" touchscreen with tuning accuracy that rivals Peterson-level studio tuners, all in a package you solder together yourself. The firmware keeps evolving after you build it, adding new display styles and features. If your audience builds pedals, plays guitar, or just likes cool maker projects, Q-Tune is the kind of thing they'll want to know about.
  </p>

  <h2>Why Q-Tune Is Different</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>The only DIY tuner pedal kit on the market.</strong> Nothing else like it exists.</li>
    <li><strong>Precision chromatic tuning</strong> that rivals dedicated studio tuners.</li>
    <li><strong>2.8" color touchscreen</strong> with customizable display styles and animated GIFs.</li>
    <li><strong>Firmware updates with USB-C</strong> add new features after you build it. It gets better over time.</li>
    <li><strong>Solderless edition coming soon!</strong> No soldering iron needed.</li>
    <li><strong>Designed by two musicians</strong> in Utah and Tennessee, not a faceless factory.</li>
  </ul>

